The Invention of Lying is a 2009 American fantasy romantic comedy film written and directed by Ricky Gervais and Matthew Robinson -LRB- in their directorial debuts -RRB- .
The film stars Gervais as the first human with the ability to lie in a world where people can only tell the truth .
The supporting cast features Jennifer Garner , Jonah Hill , Louis C.K. , Rob Lowe and Tina Fey .
The film was released in the United States on October 2 , 2009 .